response.overview: Come Summer, Come Winter, cums Harry. Looking for kinky residents to inhabit his latest series Babe Town, Harry meets eager Fanny at the station, willing to learn it all! Sex shop assistant Tanja turns out to be one of Harry’s greatest fans, and that puts our friend in just the right mood. Even pretty Sandra seems willing to move to Babe Town, although she’s got quite a surprise for Harry. But in the end nurse Jennifer has only one thing in mind, and THAT inturn is just what our horny friend wants most!
